         <div type="edition" xml:lang="ocm-Latn">
           <p>
<lb n="1"/><g type="dandaPlain">.</g><g type="dandaPlain">.</g><g type="dandaPlain">.</g><g type="floretQuatrefoil"/><g type="ddandaPlain">.</g> svasti<g type="ddandaPlain">.</g> di śakarāja <num value="1036">1036</num><g type="ddandaPlain">.</g> kāla yām̃ po ku śrī harivarmmadeva ya kumvan· yām̃ po ku śrī jaya Inravarmmadeva da<gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/>
<lb n="2"/>mvoḥ yām̃ po ku śrīśānabhadreś<supplied reason="omitted">v</supplied>ara nim̃ kā ruṅ· hanatap· Upak· chāy· pūrvvakāla trā yām̃ po ku śrī harivarmmadeva ra paṅap· Anvak· tumvrāk· ra paha<lb
n="3" break="no">tap· sā yam̃ṅ· punaḥ sā yam̃ṅ· trā ra paṅap· Anvak· pirak· ra hatap mulaṅ· di rāja nan· jem̃ dvā vvāra hatap· prāsāda yām̃ po ku śrīśānabhadreś<supplied reason="omitted">v</supplied>ara tra ra
<lb n="4"/>vuḥ suvauk· māḥ sā sarutuḥ salapan· pluḥ thil· pirak srakvak· ñū pāk· pluḥ salapan· thil dradīk· māḥ sā naṁ pluḥ dvā thil· taliy· māḥ tijuḥ tal·<!-- or read kal·? --> pradap· matā dvā
<lb n="5"/>pluḥ dvā thil· dalapan· draṁ paduḥ māḥ sā <unclear>p</unclear>aum̃<!-- or read maum̃? --> kluv· pluḥ thil· pirak <unclear>s</unclear>rakvak· ñū pāk· pluḥ thil· tralāy· māḥ sā salapan· pluḥ dalapan· thil kluv· draṁ sanraum̃ māḥ <supplied reason="lost">sā sa</supplied>
<!-- argr has checked down to here on 2021-04-05 -->
<lb n="6" break="no"/><!-- I think the syllables sā sa or sā da were already at the end of line 5, so that the veyr unclear reading at the beginning of line 6 probably needs to be changed  --> da(lapan p)luḥ dalapan thil [dalapan] draṁ vraḥ kalaśa .... kara māḥ sa ayam̃ṅ māḥ sā pāk pluh na[ṁ] thil pi[rak srakvak ñ]ū sarutuḥ thilr̥a.[pe]
<lb n="7"/>(7) nda pāk rutuḥ thil sanrauñ pirak kluv penda kluv rutuḥ dvā pluḥ thil māḥ huluv sanrauṅ dvā thil.īṇa māḥ li ..... klu(v)
<lb n="8"/>(8) salapan draṁ pirak salapan rutuḥ dalapan thil pirak si pa .... prāsāda itu māṅ sā rivuv sā ruluh salapan thil ||
           </p>
